### Tests manuels du module Rôles (nécessite un token ADMIN)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Login admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@transport.com", "password": "Admin123!" }

@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Lister (pagination + recherche)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles?page=1&limit=10&search=&sortBy=id&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Créer
# @name create
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nom": "SUPERVISEUR", "description": "Supervision des opérations" }

### Créer en double -> 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nom": "SUPERVISEUR" }

### Détail
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Modifier
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "description": "Supervision et coordination" }

### Supprimer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Supprimer un rôle utilisé (ex. ADMIN=1) -> 409
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
